headline: FactSet Declares Dividend
summary: NORWALK, Conn., Aug. 07, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- FactSet (NYSE: FDS | NASDAQ: FDS), a global financial digital platform and enterprise solutions provider, today announced that its Board of Directors approved a regular quarterly cash dividend of $1.10 per share.
